{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"I'm going to go right into the slides."},{"time":2000,"text":"And all I'm going to try and prove to you with these slides"},{"time":4000,"text":"is that I do just very straight stuff."},{"time":9000,"text":"And my ideas are --"},{"time":13000,"text":"in my head, anyway -- they're very logical"},{"time":15000,"text":"and relate to what's going on and problem solving for clients."},{"time":21000,"text":"I either convince clients at the end that I solve their problems,"},{"time":28000,"text":"or I really do solve their problems,"},{"time":30000,"text":"because usually they seem to like it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":33000,"text":"Let me go right into the slides."},{"time":37000,"text":"Can you turn off the light? Down."},{"time":42000,"text":"I like to be in the dark."},{"time":44000,"text":"I don't want you to see what I'm doing up here."}]},{"cues":[{"time":46000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":48000,"text":"Anyway, I did this house in Santa Monica,"},{"time":51000,"text":"and it got a lot of notoriety."},{"time":54000,"text":"In fact, it appeared in a porno comic book,"},{"time":57000,"text":"which is the slide on the right."}]},{"cues":[{"time":60000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":68000,"text":"This is in Venice."},{"time":71000,"text":"I just show it because I want you to know"},{"time":74000,"text":"I'm concerned about context."},{"time":76000,"text":"On the left-hand side,"},{"time":78000,"text":"I had the context of those little houses,"},{"time":81000,"text":"and I tried to build a building that fit into that context."},{"time":84000,"text":"When people take pictures of these buildings out of that context"},{"time":88000,"text":"they look really weird,"},{"time":90000,"text":"and my premise is that they make a lot more sense"},{"time":93000,"text":"when they're photographed or seen in that space."},{"time":98000,"text":"And then, once I deal with the context,"},{"time":102000,"text":"I then try to make a place that's comfortable and private and fairly serene,"},{"time":109000,"text":"as I hope you'll find that slide on the right."}]},{"cues":[{"time":114000,"text":"And then I did a law school for Loyola in downtown L.A."},{"time":120000,"text":"I was concerned about making a place for the study of law."},{"time":126000,"text":"And we continue to work with this client."},{"time":130000,"text":"The building on the right at the top is now under construction."},{"time":135000,"text":"The garage on the right -- the gray structure -- will be torn down,"},{"time":141000,"text":"finally, and several small classrooms will be placed"},{"time":145000,"text":"along this avenue that we've created, this campus."},{"time":149000,"text":"And it all related to the clients and the students"},{"time":155000,"text":"from the very first meeting saying they felt denied a place."},{"time":160000,"text":"They wanted a sense of place."},{"time":162000,"text":"And so the whole idea here was to create that kind of space"},{"time":166000,"text":"in downtown, in a neighborhood that was difficult to fit into."},{"time":173000,"text":"And it was my theory, or my point of view,"},{"time":177000,"text":"that one didn't upstage the neighborhood --"},{"time":182000,"text":"one made accommodations."},{"time":184000,"text":"I tried to be inclusive, to include the buildings in the neighborhood,"},{"time":188000,"text":"whether they were buildings I liked or not."}]},{"cues":[{"time":193000,"text":"In the '60s I started working with paper furniture"},{"time":196000,"text":"and made a bunch of stuff that was very successful in Bloomingdale's."},{"time":201000,"text":"We even made flooring, walls and everything, out of cardboard."},{"time":206000,"text":"And the success of it threw me for a loop."},{"time":210000,"text":"I couldn't deal with the success of furniture --"},{"time":212000,"text":"I wasn't secure enough as an architect --"},{"time":214000,"text":"and so I closed it all up and made furniture that nobody would like."}]},{"cues":[{"time":219000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":227000,"text":"So, nobody would like this."},{"time":229000,"text":"And it was in this, preliminary to these pieces of furniture,"},{"time":233000,"text":"that Ricky and I worked on furniture by the slice."},{"time":237000,"text":"And after we failed, I just kept failing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":241000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":249000,"text":"The piece on the left --"},{"time":251000,"text":"and that ultimately led to the piece on the right --"},{"time":254000,"text":"happened when the kid that was working on this"},{"time":257000,"text":"took one of those long strings of stuff and folded it up"},{"time":260000,"text":"to put it in the wastebasket."},{"time":262000,"text":"And I put a piece of tape around it,"},{"time":265000,"text":"as you see there, and realized you could sit on it,"},{"time":268000,"text":"and it had a lot of resilience and strength and so on."},{"time":271000,"text":"So, it was an accidental discovery."}]},{"cues":[{"time":281000,"text":"I got into fish."}]},{"cues":[{"time":284000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":291000,"text":"I mean, the story I tell is that I got mad at postmodernism -- at po-mo --"},{"time":297000,"text":"and said that fish were 500 million years earlier than man,"},{"time":303000,"text":"and if you're going to go back, we might as well go back to the beginning."},{"time":306000,"text":"And so I started making these funny things."},{"time":312000,"text":"And they started to have a life of their own and got bigger --"},{"time":318000,"text":"as the one glass at the Walker."},{"time":320000,"text":"And then, I sliced off the head and the tail and everything"},{"time":324000,"text":"and tried to translate what I was learning"},{"time":327000,"text":"about the form of the fish and the movement."},{"time":331000,"text":"And a lot of my architectural ideas that came from it --"},{"time":334000,"text":"accidental, again --"},{"time":336000,"text":"it was an intuitive kind of thing, and I just kept going with it,"},{"time":341000,"text":"and made this proposal for a building, which was only a proposal."}]},{"cues":[{"time":347000,"text":"I did this building in Japan."},{"time":352000,"text":"I was taken out to dinner after the contract"},{"time":355000,"text":"for this little restaurant was signed."},{"time":358000,"text":"And I love sake and Kobe and all that stuff."},{"time":362000,"text":"And after I got -- I was really drunk --"},{"time":368000,"text":"I was asked to do some sketches on napkins."}]},{"cues":[{"time":372000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":376000,"text":"And I made some sketches on napkins --"},{"time":380000,"text":"little boxes and Morandi-like things that I used to do."},{"time":383000,"text":"And the client said, \"Why no fish?\""},{"time":387000,"text":"And so I made a drawing with a fish, and I left Japan."},{"time":391000,"text":"Three weeks later, I received a complete set of drawings"},{"time":394000,"text":"saying we'd won the competition."}]},{"cues":[{"time":397000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":406000,"text":"Now, it's hard to do. It's hard to translate a fish form,"},{"time":411000,"text":"because they're so beautiful -- perfect --"},{"time":413000,"text":"into a building or object like this."},{"time":418000,"text":"And Oldenburg, who I work with a little once in a while,"},{"time":422000,"text":"told me I couldn't do it, and so that made it even more exciting."},{"time":430000,"text":"But he was right -- I couldn't do the tail."},{"time":433000,"text":"I started to get the head OK, but the tail I couldn't do."},{"time":437000,"text":"It was pretty hard."},{"time":439000,"text":"The thing on the right is a snake form, a ziggurat."},{"time":442000,"text":"And I put them together, and you walk between them."},{"time":445000,"text":"It was a dialog with the context again."},{"time":448000,"text":"Now, if you saw a picture of this"},{"time":451000,"text":"as it was published in Architectural Record --"},{"time":454000,"text":"they didn't show the context, so you would think,"},{"time":457000,"text":"\"God, what a pushy guy this is.\""},{"time":460000,"text":"But a friend of mine spent four hours wandering around here"},{"time":462000,"text":"looking for this restaurant."},{"time":464000,"text":"Couldn't find it."},{"time":466000,"text":"So ..."}]},{"cues":[{"time":467000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":476000,"text":"As for craft and technology and all those things"},{"time":480000,"text":"that you've all been talking about, I was thrown for a complete loop."},{"time":485000,"text":"This was built in six months."},{"time":487000,"text":"The way we sent drawings to Japan:"},{"time":491000,"text":"we used the magic computer in Michigan that does carved models,"},{"time":496000,"text":"and we used to make foam models, which that thing scanned."},{"time":500000,"text":"We made the drawings of the fish and the scales."},{"time":503000,"text":"And when I got there, everything was perfect --"},{"time":506000,"text":"except the tail."},{"time":510000,"text":"So, I decided to cut off the head and the tail."}]},{"cues":[{"time":515000,"text":"And I made the object on the left for my show at the Walker."},{"time":519000,"text":"And it's one of the nicest pieces I've ever made, I think."},{"time":522000,"text":"And then Jay Chiat, a friend and client,"},{"time":525000,"text":"asked me to do his headquarters building in L.A."},{"time":529000,"text":"For reasons we don't want to talk about, it got delayed."},{"time":535000,"text":"Toxic waste, I guess, is the key clue to that one."},{"time":540000,"text":"And so we built a temporary building -- I'm getting good at temporary --"},{"time":546000,"text":"and we put a conference room in that's a fish."}]},{"cues":[{"time":551000,"text":"And, finally, Jay dragged me to my hometown, Toronto, Canada."},{"time":556000,"text":"And there is a story -- it's a real story -- about my grandmother"},{"time":560000,"text":"buying a carp on Thursday, bringing it home,"},{"time":562000,"text":"putting it in the bathtub when I was a kid."},{"time":564000,"text":"I played with it in the evening."},{"time":566000,"text":"When I went to sleep, the next day it wasn't there."},{"time":569000,"text":"And the next night, we had gefilte fish."}]},{"cues":[{"time":571000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":573000,"text":"And so I set up this interior for Jay's offices"},{"time":579000,"text":"and I made a pedestal for a sculpture."},{"time":581000,"text":"And he didn't buy a sculpture, so I made one."},{"time":585000,"text":"I went around Toronto and found a bathtub like my grandmother's,"},{"time":588000,"text":"and I put the fish in."},{"time":590000,"text":"It was a joke."}]},{"cues":[{"time":593000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":599000,"text":"I play with funny people like [Claes] Oldenburg."},{"time":603000,"text":"We've been friends for a long time."},{"time":606000,"text":"And we've started to work on things."},{"time":611000,"text":"A few years ago, we did a performance piece in Venice, Italy,"},{"time":615000,"text":"called \"Il Corso del Coltello\" -- the Swiss Army knife."},{"time":622000,"text":"And most of the imagery is --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":625000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":628000,"text":"Claes', but those two little boys are my sons,"},{"time":631000,"text":"and they were Claes' assistants in the play."},{"time":635000,"text":"He was the Swiss Army knife."},{"time":638000,"text":"He was a souvenir salesman who always wanted to be a painter,"},{"time":642000,"text":"and I was Frankie P. Toronto."},{"time":644000,"text":"P for Palladio."},{"time":646000,"text":"Dressed up like the AT&amp;T building by Claes --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":650000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":653000,"text":"with a fish hat."},{"time":657000,"text":"The highlight of the performance was at the end."},{"time":661000,"text":"This beautiful object, the Swiss Army knife,"},{"time":664000,"text":"which I get credit for participating in."},{"time":667000,"text":"And I can tell you -- it's totally an Oldenburg."},{"time":670000,"text":"I had nothing to do with it."},{"time":671000,"text":"The only thing I did was, I made it possible for them"},{"time":674000,"text":"to turn those blades so you could sail this thing in the canal,"},{"time":677000,"text":"because I love sailing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":679000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":681000,"text":"We made it into a sailing craft."}]},{"cues":[{"time":684000,"text":"I've been known to mess with things like chain link fencing."},{"time":687000,"text":"I do it because it's a curious thing in the culture,"},{"time":691000,"text":"when things are made in such great quantities,"},{"time":694000,"text":"absorbed in such great quantities,"},{"time":696000,"text":"and there's so much denial about them."},{"time":698000,"text":"People hate it."},{"time":700000,"text":"And I'm fascinated with that, which, like the paper furniture --"},{"time":704000,"text":"it's one of those materials."},{"time":706000,"text":"And I'm always drawn to that."},{"time":708000,"text":"And so I did a lot of dirty things with chain link,"},{"time":711000,"text":"which nobody will forgive me for."},{"time":713000,"text":"But Claes made homage to it in the Loyola Law School."},{"time":717000,"text":"And that chain link is really expensive."},{"time":719000,"text":"It's in perspective and everything."}]},{"cues":[{"time":724000,"text":"And then we did a camp together for children with cancer."},{"time":728000,"text":"And you can see, we started making a building together."},{"time":732000,"text":"Of course, the milk can is his."},{"time":735000,"text":"But we were trying to collide our ideas,"},{"time":737000,"text":"to put objects next to each other."},{"time":739000,"text":"Like a Morandi -- like the little bottles -- composing them like a still life."},{"time":744000,"text":"And it seemed to work as a way to put he and I together."}]},{"cues":[{"time":753000,"text":"Then Jay Chiat asked me to do this building"},{"time":757000,"text":"on this funny lot in Venice, and I started with this three-piece thing,"},{"time":763000,"text":"and you entered in the middle."},{"time":765000,"text":"And Jay asked me what I was going to do with the piece in the middle."},{"time":768000,"text":"And he pushed that."},{"time":770000,"text":"And one day I had a -- oh, well, the other way."},{"time":773000,"text":"I had the binoculars from Claes, and I put them there,"},{"time":776000,"text":"and I could never get rid of them after that."},{"time":782000,"text":"Oldenburg made the binoculars incredible"},{"time":785000,"text":"when he sent me the first model of the real proposal."},{"time":790000,"text":"It made my building look sick."},{"time":792000,"text":"And it was this interaction between"},{"time":794000,"text":"that kind of, up-the-ante stuff that became pretty interesting."},{"time":799000,"text":"It led to the building on the left."},{"time":801000,"text":"And I still think the Time magazine picture will be of the binoculars, you know,"},{"time":805000,"text":"leaving out the -- what the hell."}]},{"cues":[{"time":815000,"text":"I use a lot of metal in my work,"},{"time":817000,"text":"and I have a hard time connecting with the craft."},{"time":821000,"text":"The whole thing about my house,"},{"time":824000,"text":"the whole use of rough carpentry and everything,"},{"time":827000,"text":"was the frustration with the crafts available."},{"time":830000,"text":"I said, \"If I can't get the craft that I want,"},{"time":834000,"text":"I'll use the craft I can get.\""},{"time":836000,"text":"There were plenty of models for that,"},{"time":838000,"text":"in Rauschenberg and Jasper Johns, and many artists"},{"time":841000,"text":"who were making beautiful art and sculpture with junk materials."},{"time":848000,"text":"I went into the metal because it was a way of building a building"},{"time":851000,"text":"that was a sculpture."},{"time":855000,"text":"And it was all of one material,"},{"time":857000,"text":"and the metal could go on the roof as well as the walls."},{"time":860000,"text":"The metalworkers, for the most part,"},{"time":863000,"text":"do ducts behind the ceilings and stuff."},{"time":866000,"text":"I was given an opportunity to design an exhibit"},{"time":869000,"text":"for the metalworkers' unions of America and Canada in Washington,"},{"time":876000,"text":"and I did it on the condition that they become my partners"},{"time":878000,"text":"in the future and help me with all future metal buildings, etc. etc."},{"time":884000,"text":"And it's working very well"},{"time":886000,"text":"to have these people, these craftsmen, interested in it."},{"time":889000,"text":"I just tell the stories."},{"time":891000,"text":"It's a way of connecting, at least, with some of those people"},{"time":896000,"text":"that are so important to the realization of architecture."}]},{"cues":[{"time":905000,"text":"The metal continued into a building -- Herman Miller, in Sacramento."},{"time":911000,"text":"And it's just a complex of factory buildings."},{"time":915000,"text":"And Herman Miller has this philosophy of having a place --"},{"time":920000,"text":"a people place."},{"time":922000,"text":"I mean, it's kind of a trite thing to say,"},{"time":925000,"text":"but it is real that they wanted to have a central place"},{"time":929000,"text":"where the cafeteria would be, where the people would come"},{"time":933000,"text":"and where the people working would interact."},{"time":938000,"text":"So it's out in the middle of nowhere, and you approach it."},{"time":943000,"text":"It's copper and galvanize."},{"time":946000,"text":"I used the galvanize and copper"},{"time":949000,"text":"in a very light gauge, so it would buckle."},{"time":953000,"text":"I spent a lot of time undoing Richard Meier's aesthetic."},{"time":960000,"text":"Everybody's trying to get the panels perfect,"},{"time":962000,"text":"and I always try to get them sloppy and fuzzy."},{"time":966000,"text":"And they end up looking like stone."},{"time":969000,"text":"This is the central area."},{"time":971000,"text":"There's a ramp."}]},{"cues":[{"time":973000,"text":"And that little dome in there is a building by Stanley Tigerman."},{"time":976000,"text":"Stanley was instrumental in my getting this job."},{"time":979000,"text":"And when I was awarded the contract I, at the very beginning,"},{"time":983000,"text":"asked the client if they would let Stanley do a cameo piece with me."},{"time":988000,"text":"Because these were ideas that we were talking about,"},{"time":992000,"text":"building things next to each other, making --"},{"time":995000,"text":"it's all about [a] metaphor for a city, maybe."},{"time":997000,"text":"And so Stanley did the little dome thing."},{"time":1000000,"text":"And we did it over the phone and by fax."},{"time":1002000,"text":"He would send me a fax and show me something."},{"time":1005000,"text":"He'd made a building with a dome and he had a little tower."},{"time":1008000,"text":"I told him, \"No, no, that's too ongepotchket."},{"time":1011000,"text":"I don't want the tower.\""},{"time":1015000,"text":"So he came back with a simpler building,"},{"time":1019000,"text":"but he put some funny details on it,"},{"time":1025000,"text":"and he moved it closer to my building."},{"time":1029000,"text":"And so I decided to put him in a depression."},{"time":1033000,"text":"I put him in a hole and made a kind of a hole that he sits in."},{"time":1037000,"text":"And so then he put two bridges -- this all happened on the fax,"},{"time":1041000,"text":"going back and forth over a couple of weeks' period."},{"time":1043000,"text":"And he put these two bridges with pink guardrails on it."},{"time":1047000,"text":"And so then I put this big billboard behind it."},{"time":1050000,"text":"And I call it, \"David and Goliath.\""},{"time":1056000,"text":"And that's my cafeteria."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1063000,"text":"In Boston, we had that old building on the left."},{"time":1068000,"text":"It was a very prominent building off the freeway,"},{"time":1071000,"text":"and we added a floor and cleaned it up and fixed it up"},{"time":1075000,"text":"and used the kind of -- I thought -- the language of the neighborhood,"},{"time":1080000,"text":"which had these cornices, projecting cornices."},{"time":1084000,"text":"Mine got a little exuberant, but I used lead copper,"},{"time":1091000,"text":"which is a beautiful material, and it turns green in 100 years."},{"time":1096000,"text":"Instead of, like, copper in 10 or 15."},{"time":1102000,"text":"We redid the side of the building"},{"time":1104000,"text":"and re-proportioned the windows so it sort of fit into the space."},{"time":1108000,"text":"And it surprised both Boston and myself that we got it approved,"},{"time":1112000,"text":"because they have very strict kind of design guideline,"},{"time":1118000,"text":"and they wouldn't normally think I would fit them."},{"time":1123000,"text":"The detailing was very careful with the lead copper"},{"time":1126000,"text":"and making panels and fitting it tightly"},{"time":1132000,"text":"into the fabric of the existing building."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1138000,"text":"In Barcelona, on Las Ramblas for some film festival,"},{"time":1144000,"text":"I did the Hollywood sign going and coming,"},{"time":1147000,"text":"made a building out of it, and they built it."},{"time":1150000,"text":"I flew in one night and took this picture."},{"time":1153000,"text":"But they made it a third smaller than my model without telling me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1160000,"text":"And then more metal and some chain link in Santa Monica --"},{"time":1166000,"text":"a little shopping center."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1173000,"text":"And this is a laser laboratory at the University of Iowa,"},{"time":1178000,"text":"in which the fish comes back as an abstraction in the back."},{"time":1182000,"text":"It's the support labs, which, by some coincidence, required no windows."},{"time":1195000,"text":"And the shape fit perfectly."},{"time":1200000,"text":"I just joined the points."},{"time":1202000,"text":"In the curved part there's all the mechanical equipment."},{"time":1206000,"text":"That solid wall behind it is a pipe chase -- a pipe canyon --"},{"time":1211000,"text":"and so it was an opportunity that I seized,"},{"time":1214000,"text":"because I didn't have to have any protruding ducts or vents or things in this form."},{"time":1220000,"text":"It gave me an opportunity to make a sculpture out of it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1225000,"text":"This is a small house somewhere."},{"time":1232000,"text":"They've been building it so long I don't remember where it is."},{"time":1235000,"text":"It's in the West Valley."},{"time":1237000,"text":"And we started with the stream"},{"time":1241000,"text":"and built the house along the stream -- dammed it up to make a lake."},{"time":1246000,"text":"These are the models."},{"time":1251000,"text":"The reality, with the lake --"},{"time":1254000,"text":"the workmanship is pretty bad."},{"time":1258000,"text":"And it reminded me why I play defensively in things like my house."},{"time":1264000,"text":"When you have to do something really cheaply,"},{"time":1268000,"text":"it's hard to get perfect corners and stuff."},{"time":1284000,"text":"That big metal thing is a passage, and in it is --"},{"time":1290000,"text":"you go downstairs into the living room and then down into the bedroom,"},{"time":1293000,"text":"which is on the right."},{"time":1301000,"text":"It's kind of like a whole built town."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1308000,"text":"I was asked to do a hospital for schizophrenic adolescents at Yale."},{"time":1315000,"text":"I thought it was fitting for me to be doing that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1324000,"text":"This is a house next to a Philip Johnson house in Minnesota."},{"time":1330000,"text":"The owners had a dilemma -- they asked Philip to do it."},{"time":1334000,"text":"He was too busy."},{"time":1337000,"text":"He didn't recommend me, by the way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1340000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1342000,"text":"We ended up having to make it a sculpture, because the dilemma was,"},{"time":1348000,"text":"how do you build a building that doesn't look like the language?"},{"time":1351000,"text":"Is it going to look like this beautiful estate is sub-divided?"},{"time":1355000,"text":"Etc. etc."},{"time":1357000,"text":"You've got the idea."},{"time":1359000,"text":"And so we finally ended up making it."},{"time":1361000,"text":"These people are art collectors."},{"time":1363000,"text":"And we finally made it so it appears very sculptural"},{"time":1367000,"text":"from the main house and all the windows are on the other side."},{"time":1375000,"text":"And the building is very sculptural as you walk around it."},{"time":1380000,"text":"It's made of metal and the brown stuff is Fin-Ply --"},{"time":1386000,"text":"it's that formed lumber from Finland."},{"time":1390000,"text":"We used it at Loyola on the chapel, and it didn't work."},{"time":1393000,"text":"I keep trying to make it work."},{"time":1395000,"text":"In this case we learned how to detail it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1401000,"text":"In Cleveland, there's Burnham Mall, on the left."},{"time":1408000,"text":"It's never been finished."},{"time":1410000,"text":"Going out to the lake, you can see all those new buildings we built."},{"time":1415000,"text":"And we had the opportunity to build a building on this site."},{"time":1421000,"text":"There's a railroad track."},{"time":1423000,"text":"This is the city hall over here somewhere, and the courthouse."},{"time":1428000,"text":"And the centerline of the mall goes out."},{"time":1432000,"text":"Burnham had designed a railroad station that was never built,"},{"time":1437000,"text":"and so we followed."},{"time":1439000,"text":"Sohio is on the axis here,"},{"time":1441000,"text":"and we followed the axis, and they're two kind of goalposts."},{"time":1444000,"text":"And this is our building,"},{"time":1446000,"text":"which is a corporate headquarters for an insurance company."},{"time":1450000,"text":"We collaborated with Oldenburg and put the newspaper on top, folded."},{"time":1461000,"text":"The health club is fastened to the garage"},{"time":1465000,"text":"with a C-clamp, for Cleveland."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1468000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1470000,"text":"You drive down."},{"time":1472000,"text":"So it's about a 10-story C-clamp."},{"time":1475000,"text":"And all this stuff at the bottom is a museum,"},{"time":1478000,"text":"and an idea for a very fancy automobile entry."},{"time":1482000,"text":"This owner has a pet peeve about bad automobile entries."},{"time":1486000,"text":"And this would be a hotel."},{"time":1488000,"text":"So, the centerline of this thing -- we'd preserve it,"},{"time":1490000,"text":"and it would start to work with the scale of the new buildings"},{"time":1494000,"text":"by Pelli and Kohn Pederson Fox, etc., that are underway."},{"time":1510000,"text":"It's hard to do high-rise."},{"time":1512000,"text":"I feel much more comfortable down here."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1516000,"text":"This is a piece of property in Brentwood."},{"time":1519000,"text":"And a long time ago, about '82 or something, after my house --"},{"time":1525000,"text":"I designed a house for myself"},{"time":1528000,"text":"that would be a village of several pavilions around a courtyard --"},{"time":1533000,"text":"and the owner of this lot worked for me"},{"time":1538000,"text":"and built that actual model on the left."},{"time":1540000,"text":"And she came back,"},{"time":1542000,"text":"I guess wealthier or something -- something happened --"},{"time":1546000,"text":"and asked me to design a house for her on this site."},{"time":1554000,"text":"And following that basic idea of the village,"},{"time":1559000,"text":"we changed it as we got into it."},{"time":1561000,"text":"I locked the house into the site by cutting the back end --"},{"time":1566000,"text":"here you see on the photographs of the site --"},{"time":1569000,"text":"slicing into it and putting all the bathrooms and dressing rooms"},{"time":1573000,"text":"like a retaining wall, creating a lower level zone for the master bedroom,"},{"time":1578000,"text":"which I designed like a kind of a barge,"},{"time":1581000,"text":"looking like a boat."},{"time":1585000,"text":"And that's it, built."},{"time":1592000,"text":"The dome was a request from the client."},{"time":1596000,"text":"She wanted a dome somewhere in the house."},{"time":1598000,"text":"She didn't care where."},{"time":1600000,"text":"When you sleep in this bedroom, I hope --"},{"time":1602000,"text":"I mean, I haven't slept in it yet."},{"time":1605000,"text":"I've offered to marry her so I could sleep there,"},{"time":1609000,"text":"but she said I didn't have to do that."},{"time":1617000,"text":"But when you're in that room,"},{"time":1620000,"text":"you feel like you're on a kind of barge on some kind of lake."},{"time":1624000,"text":"And it's very private."},{"time":1626000,"text":"The landscape is being built around to create a private garden."},{"time":1629000,"text":"And then up above there's a garden on this side of the living room,"},{"time":1634000,"text":"and one on the other side."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1639000,"text":"These aren't focused very well."},{"time":1641000,"text":"I don't know how to do it from here."},{"time":1645000,"text":"Focus the one on the right."},{"time":1649000,"text":"It's up there."},{"time":1651000,"text":"Left -- it's my right."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1655000,"text":"Anyway, you enter into a garden with a beautiful grove of trees."},{"time":1661000,"text":"That's the living room."},{"time":1663000,"text":"Servants' quarters."},{"time":1665000,"text":"A guest bedroom, which has this dome with marble on it."},{"time":1669000,"text":"And then you enter into the living room and then so on."},{"time":1679000,"text":"This is the bedroom."},{"time":1681000,"text":"You come down from this level along the stairway,"},{"time":1683000,"text":"and you enter the bedroom here, going into the lake."},{"time":1686000,"text":"And the bed is back in this space,"},{"time":1688000,"text":"with windows looking out onto the lake."},{"time":1691000,"text":"These Stonehenge things were designed to give foreground"},{"time":1696000,"text":"and to create a greater depth in this shallow lot."},{"time":1700000,"text":"The material is lead copper, like in the building in Boston."},{"time":1709000,"text":"And so it was an intent to make this small piece of land --"},{"time":1714000,"text":"it's 100 by 250 -- into a kind of an estate by separating these areas"},{"time":1720000,"text":"and making the living room and dining room into this pavilion"},{"time":1726000,"text":"with a high space in it."},{"time":1733000,"text":"And this happened by accident that I got this right on axis"},{"time":1736000,"text":"with the dining room table."},{"time":1740000,"text":"It looks like I got a Baldessari painting for free."},{"time":1745000,"text":"But the idea is, the windows are all placed"},{"time":1747000,"text":"so you see pieces of the house outside."},{"time":1751000,"text":"Eventually this will be screened -- these trees will come up --"},{"time":1755000,"text":"and it will be very private."},{"time":1757000,"text":"And you feel like you're in your own kind of village."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1765000,"text":"This is for Michael Eisner -- Disney."},{"time":1770000,"text":"We're doing some work for him."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1773000,"text":"And this is in Anaheim, California, and it's a freeway building."},{"time":1778000,"text":"You go under this bridge at about 65 miles an hour,"},{"time":1782000,"text":"and there's another bridge here."},{"time":1784000,"text":"And you're through this room in a split second,"},{"time":1786000,"text":"and the building will sort of reflect that."},{"time":1788000,"text":"On the backside, it's much more humane -- entrance,"},{"time":1791000,"text":"dining hall, etc."},{"time":1793000,"text":"And then this thing here -- I'm hoping as you drive by you'll hear"},{"time":1798000,"text":"the picket fence effect of the sound hitting it."},{"time":1802000,"text":"Kind of a fun thing to do."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1808000,"text":"I'm doing a building in Switzerland, Basel,"},{"time":1812000,"text":"which is an office building for a furniture company."},{"time":1815000,"text":"And we struggled with the image."},{"time":1818000,"text":"These are the early studies, but they have to sell furniture"},{"time":1821000,"text":"to normal people, so if I did the building and it was too fancy,"},{"time":1826000,"text":"then people might say, \"Well, the furniture looks OK in his thing,"},{"time":1830000,"text":"but no, it ain't going to look good in my normal building.\""},{"time":1832000,"text":"So we've made a kind of pragmatic slab in the second phase here,"},{"time":1836000,"text":"and we've taken the conference facilities and made a villa out of them"},{"time":1840000,"text":"so that the communal space is very sculptural and separate."},{"time":1844000,"text":"And you're looking at it from the offices and you create a kind of"},{"time":1848000,"text":"interaction between these pieces."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1852000,"text":"This is in Paris, along the Seine."},{"time":1856000,"text":"Palais des Sports, the Gare de Lyon over here."},{"time":1860000,"text":"The Minister of Finance -- the guy that moved from the Louvre -- goes in here."},{"time":1864000,"text":"There's a new library across the river."},{"time":1867000,"text":"And back in here, in this already treed park,"},{"time":1871000,"text":"we're doing a very dense building called the American Center,"},{"time":1875000,"text":"which has a theater, apartments, dance school, an art museum,"},{"time":1882000,"text":"restaurants and all kinds of -- it's a very dense program --"},{"time":1886000,"text":"bookstores, etc."},{"time":1889000,"text":"In a very tight, small --"},{"time":1891000,"text":"this is the ground level."},{"time":1894000,"text":"And the French have this extraordinary way of screwing things up"},{"time":1897000,"text":"by taking a beautiful site and cutting the corner off."},{"time":1901000,"text":"They call it the plan coupe."},{"time":1903000,"text":"And I struggled with that thing --"},{"time":1909000,"text":"how to get around the corner."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1911000,"text":"These are the models for it."},{"time":1914000,"text":"I showed you the other model, the one --"},{"time":1922000,"text":"this is the way I organized myself so I could make the drawing --"},{"time":1925000,"text":"so I understood the problem."},{"time":1931000,"text":"I was trying to get around this plan coupe -- how do you do it?"},{"time":1935000,"text":"Apartments, etc."},{"time":1938000,"text":"And these are the kind of study models we did."},{"time":1940000,"text":"And the one on the left is pretty awful."},{"time":1944000,"text":"You can see why I was ready to commit suicide when this one was built."},{"time":1949000,"text":"But out of it came finally this resolution, where the elevator piece"},{"time":1956000,"text":"worked frontally to this, parallel to this street,"},{"time":1959000,"text":"and also parallel to here."},{"time":1961000,"text":"And then this kind of twist, with this balcony and the skirt,"},{"time":1965000,"text":"kind of like a ballerina lifting her skirt to let you into the foyer."},{"time":1971000,"text":"The restaurants here -- the apartments and the theater, etc."},{"time":1974000,"text":"So it would all be built in stone, in French limestone,"},{"time":1978000,"text":"except for this metal piece."},{"time":1980000,"text":"And it faces into a park."},{"time":1983000,"text":"And the idea was to make this express the energy of this."},{"time":1991000,"text":"On the side facing the street it's much more normal,"},{"time":1995000,"text":"except I slipped a few mansards down, so that coming on the point,"},{"time":2001000,"text":"these housing units made a gesture to the corner."},{"time":2014000,"text":"And this will be some kind of high-tech billboard."},{"time":2019000,"text":"If any of you guys have any ideas for it, please contact me."},{"time":2021000,"text":"I don't know what to do."}]},{"cues":[{"time":2026000,"text":"Jay Chiat is a glutton for punishment, and he hired me"},{"time":2029000,"text":"to do a house for him in the Hamptons."},{"time":2031000,"text":"And it's got a fish."},{"time":2033000,"text":"And I keep thinking, \"This is going to be the last fish.\""},{"time":2036000,"text":"It's like a drug addict."},{"time":2039000,"text":"I say, \"I'm not going to do it anymore -- I don't want to do it anymore --"},{"time":2041000,"text":"I'm not going to do it.\""},{"time":2043000,"text":"And then I do it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":2045000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":2046000,"text":"There it is."},{"time":2047000,"text":"But it's the living room."},{"time":2048000,"text":"And this piece here is --"},{"time":2050000,"text":"I don't know what it is."},{"time":2052000,"text":"I just added it so that we'd have enough money in the budget"},{"time":2054000,"text":"so we could take something out."}]},{"cues":[{"time":2057000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":2065000,"text":"This is Euro Disney, and I've worked with all of the guys"},{"time":2069000,"text":"that presented to you earlier."},{"time":2072000,"text":"We've had a lot of fun working together."},{"time":2074000,"text":"I think I'm from Mars for them, and they are for me,"},{"time":2078000,"text":"but somehow we all manage to work together,"},{"time":2081000,"text":"and I think, productively."},{"time":2085000,"text":"So far."},{"time":2087000,"text":"This is a shopping thing."},{"time":2090000,"text":"You come into the Magic Kingdom"},{"time":2093000,"text":"and the hotel that Tony Baxter's group is doing out here."},{"time":2097000,"text":"And then this is a kind of a shopping mall,"},{"time":2100000,"text":"with a rodeo and restaurants."},{"time":2103000,"text":"And another restaurant."},{"time":2106000,"text":"What I did -- because of the Paris skies being quite dull,"},{"time":2111000,"text":"I made a light grid that's perpendicular to the train station,"},{"time":2114000,"text":"to the route of the train."},{"time":2116000,"text":"It looks like it's kind of been there,"},{"time":2119000,"text":"and then crashed all these simpler forms into it."},{"time":2123000,"text":"The light grid will have a light, be lit up at night and give a"},{"time":2129000,"text":"kind of light ceiling."},{"time":2140000,"text":"In Switzerland -- Germany, actually -- on the Rhine across from Basel,"},{"time":2144000,"text":"we did a furniture factory and a furniture museum."}]},{"cues":[{"time":2148000,"text":"And I tried to -- there's a Nick Grimshaw building over here,"},{"time":2151000,"text":"there's an Oldenburg sculpture over here --"},{"time":2154000,"text":"I tried to make a relationship urbanistically."},{"time":2158000,"text":"And I don't gave good slides to show -- it's just been completed --"},{"time":2161000,"text":"but this piece here is this building, and these pieces here and here."},{"time":2165000,"text":"And as you pass by it's always part -- you see it as all of these pieces"},{"time":2170000,"text":"accrue and become part of an overall neighborhood."},{"time":2180000,"text":"It's plaster and just zinc."},{"time":2183000,"text":"And you wonder, if this is a museum,"},{"time":2186000,"text":"what it's going to be like inside?"},{"time":2188000,"text":"If it's going to be so busy and crazy that you wouldn't show anything,"},{"time":2192000,"text":"and just wait."},{"time":2194000,"text":"I'm so cunning and clever -- I made it quiet and wonderful."},{"time":2199000,"text":"But on the outside it does scream out at you a bit."},{"time":2207000,"text":"It's actually basically three square rooms"},{"time":2212000,"text":"with a couple of skylights and stuff."},{"time":2214000,"text":"And from the building in the back, you see it as"},{"time":2217000,"text":"an iceberg floating by in the hills."},{"time":2223000,"text":"I know I'm over time."},{"time":2241000,"text":"See, that skylight goes down and becomes that one."},{"time":2244000,"text":"So it's pretty quiet inside."}]},{"cues":[{"time":2251000,"text":"This is the Disney Hall -- the concert hall."},{"time":2255000,"text":"It's a complicated project."},{"time":2259000,"text":"It has a chamber hall."},{"time":2261000,"text":"It's related to an existing Chandler Pavilion that was built"},{"time":2265000,"text":"with a lot of love and tears and caring."},{"time":2268000,"text":"And it's not a great building, but I approached it optimistically,"},{"time":2273000,"text":"that we would make a compositional relationship between us"},{"time":2281000,"text":"that would strengthen both of us."},{"time":2284000,"text":"And the plan of this -- it's a concert hall."},{"time":2286000,"text":"This is the foyer, which is kind of a garden structure."},{"time":2289000,"text":"There's commercial at the ground floor."},{"time":2291000,"text":"These are offices, which, really, in the competition,"},{"time":2295000,"text":"we didn't have to design."},{"time":2297000,"text":"But finally, there's a hotel there."},{"time":2301000,"text":"These were the kind of relationships made to the Chandler,"},{"time":2306000,"text":"composing these elevations together and relating them"},{"time":2310000,"text":"to the buildings that existed -- to MOCA, etc."}]},{"cues":[{"time":2319000,"text":"The acoustician in the competition gave us criteria,"},{"time":2324000,"text":"which led to this compartmentalized scheme,"},{"time":2328000,"text":"which we found out after the competition would not work at all."},{"time":2332000,"text":"But everybody liked these forms and liked the space,"},{"time":2337000,"text":"and so that's one of the problems of a competition."},{"time":2339000,"text":"You have to then try and get that back in some way."},{"time":2345000,"text":"And we studied many models."},{"time":2349000,"text":"This was our original model."},{"time":2351000,"text":"These were the three buildings that were the ideal --"},{"time":2355000,"text":"the Concertgebouw, Boston and Berlin."},{"time":2358000,"text":"Everybody liked the surround."},{"time":2361000,"text":"Actually, this is the smallest hall in size,"},{"time":2364000,"text":"and it has more seats than any of these"},{"time":2367000,"text":"because it has double balconies."},{"time":2369000,"text":"Our client doesn't want balconies, so --"},{"time":2372000,"text":"and when we met our new acoustician, he told us"},{"time":2374000,"text":"this was the right shape or this was the right shape."},{"time":2377000,"text":"And we tried many shapes, trying to get the energy"},{"time":2381000,"text":"of the original design within an acoustical, acceptable format."},{"time":2389000,"text":"We finally settled on a shape that was"},{"time":2391000,"text":"the proportion of the Concertgebouw"},{"time":2394000,"text":"with the sloping outside walls, which the acoustician said"},{"time":2399000,"text":"were crucial to this and later decided they weren't,"},{"time":2402000,"text":"but now we have them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":2404000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":2406000,"text":"And our idea is to make the seating carriage very sculptural"},{"time":2411000,"text":"and out of wood and like a big boat sitting in this plaster room."},{"time":2417000,"text":"That's the idea."},{"time":2419000,"text":"And the corners would have skylights"},{"time":2425000,"text":"and these columns would be structural."},{"time":2429000,"text":"And the nice thing about introducing columns is they give you a"},{"time":2432000,"text":"kind of sense of proscenium from wherever you sit,"},{"time":2435000,"text":"and create intimacy."},{"time":2437000,"text":"Now, this is not a final design -- these are just on the way to being --"},{"time":2442000,"text":"and so I wouldn't take it literally, except the feeling of the space."},{"time":2448000,"text":"We studied the acoustics with laser stuff,"},{"time":2453000,"text":"and they bounce them off this and see where it all works."},{"time":2456000,"text":"But you get the sense of the hall in section."},{"time":2458000,"text":"Most halls come straight down into a proscenium."},{"time":2464000,"text":"In this case we're opening it back up"},{"time":2466000,"text":"and getting skylights in the four corners."},{"time":2469000,"text":"And so it will be quite a different shape."}]},{"cues":[{"time":2476000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":2478000,"text":"The original building, because it was frog-like,"},{"time":2483000,"text":"fit nicely on the site and cranked itself well."},{"time":2486000,"text":"When you get into a box, it's harder to do it -- and here we are,"},{"time":2489000,"text":"struggling with how to put the hotel in."},{"time":2491000,"text":"And this is a teapot I designed for Alessi."},{"time":2494000,"text":"I just stuck it on there."},{"time":2497000,"text":"But this is how I do work. I do take pieces and bits and look at it"},{"time":2502000,"text":"and struggle with it and cut it away."},{"time":2504000,"text":"And of course it's not going to look like that,"},{"time":2506000,"text":"but it is the crazy way I tend to work."}]},{"cues":[{"time":2511000,"text":"And then finally, in L.A. I was asked to do a sculpture"},{"time":2514000,"text":"at the foot of Interstate Bank Tower, the highest building in L.A."},{"time":2520000,"text":"Larry Halprin is doing the stairs."},{"time":2523000,"text":"And I was asked to do a fish, and so I did a snake."}]},{"cues":[{"time":2527000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":2528000,"text":"It's a public space, and I made it kind of a garden structure,"},{"time":2531000,"text":"and you can go in it."},{"time":2533000,"text":"It's a kiva, and Larry's putting some water in there,"},{"time":2536000,"text":"and it works much better than a fish."}]},{"cues":[{"time":2539000,"text":"In Barcelona I was asked to do a fish, and we're working on that,"},{"time":2544000,"text":"at the foot of a Ritz-Carlton Tower being done by"},{"time":2547000,"text":"Skidmore, Owings and Merrill."},{"time":2549000,"text":"And the Ritz-Carlton Tower is being designed with exposed steel,"},{"time":2552000,"text":"non-fire proof, much like those old gas tanks."},{"time":2556000,"text":"And so we took the language of this exposed steel and used it,"},{"time":2562000,"text":"perverted it, into the form of the fish, and created a kind of"},{"time":2570000,"text":"a 19th-century contraption that looks like, that will sit --"},{"time":2575000,"text":"this is the beach and the harbor out in front,"},{"time":2577000,"text":"and this is really a shopping center with department stores."},{"time":2581000,"text":"And we split these bridges."},{"time":2583000,"text":"Originally, this was all solid with a hole in it."},{"time":2585000,"text":"We cut them loose and made several bridges and created a kind of"},{"time":2590000,"text":"a foreground for this hotel."},{"time":2592000,"text":"We showed this to the hotel people the other day,"},{"time":2595000,"text":"and they were terrified and said that nobody would come"},{"time":2600000,"text":"to the Ritz-Carlton anymore, because of this fish."}]},{"cues":[{"time":2605000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":2614000,"text":"And finally, I just threw these in -- Lou Danziger."},{"time":2616000,"text":"I didn't expect Lou Danziger to be here,"},{"time":2618000,"text":"but this is a building I did for him in 1964, I think."},{"time":2622000,"text":"A little studio -- and it's sadly for sale."},{"time":2626000,"text":"Time goes on."}]},{"cues":[{"time":2628000,"text":"And this is my son working with me on a small fast-food thing."},{"time":2635000,"text":"He designed the robot as the cashier, and the head moves,"},{"time":2638000,"text":"and I did the rest of it."},{"time":2640000,"text":"And the food wasn't as good as the stuff, and so it failed."},{"time":2644000,"text":"It should have been the other way around --"},{"time":2645000,"text":"the food should have been good first."},{"time":2647000,"text":"It didn't work."}]},{"cues":[{"time":2648000,"text":"Thank you very much."}]}]}